addKey(address,address,uint256,uint8,byt.details: Add publicKey to list for a Name

params._nonce: The signed uint256 nonce (should be Name's current nonce + 1)
params._signatureR: The R part of the signature
params._signatureS: The S part of the signature
params._signatureV: The V part of the signature

getDefaultKey(address).details: Get default public key of a Name

getKeys(address,uint256,uint256).details: Get list of publicKeys of a Name

getTotalPublicKeysCount(address).details: Get total publicKeys count for a Name

initialize(address,address).details: Store the PublicKey info for a Name

params._defaultKey: The default public key for this Name

isExist(address).details: Check whether or not a Name ID exist in the list of Public Keys

isKeyExist(address,address).details: Check whether or not a publicKey exist in the list for a Name

setDefaultKey(address,address,uint8,byte.details: Set a publicKey as the default for a Name

params._signatureR: The R part of the signature for this update
params._signatureS: The S part of the signature for this update
params._signatureV: The V part of the signature for this update

setNameAccountRecoveryAddress(address).details: The AO set the NameAccountRecovery Address

setWhitelist(address,bool).details: Whitelist `_account` address to transact on behalf of others

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfer ownership of The AO to new address

params._theAO: The new address to be transferred

whitelistAddKey(address,address).details: Whitelisted address add publicKey to list for a Name
